# Prompt Generator Overhaul — PRD Implementation

Align the Prompt Generator frontend with the PRD three-layer architecture. The backend engine ([generatorService.js](file:///f:/PROMPTLAB/src/services/generatorService.js)) already implements the full system — the work is **entirely frontend wiring and UI**.

## Current Issues

1. **[generatePrompt()](file:///f:/PROMPTLAB/public/js/app.js#179-226) crash** — references non-existent `#generatorIntent` element (removed from HTML)
2. **Wrong property name** — uses `genResult.improvedPrompt` but service returns `finalPrompt`
3. **Stub renderer** — [renderGeneratorResults](file:///f:/PROMPTLAB/public/js/app.js#581-598) is 16 lines, ignores intent/blueprint/scores/explanation
4. **No progress indicator** — no visual feedback during the INTENT → BLUEPRINT → GENERATE → SCORE pipeline

## Proposed Changes

### Frontend Logic

#### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///f:/PROMPTLAB/public/js/app.js)

**[generatePrompt()](file:///f:/PROMPTLAB/public/js/app.js#179-226) (lines 179-225):**
- Remove `#generatorIntent` reference (PRD: intent inference is silent)
- Pass the full `genResult` object to the renderer (intent, blueprint, v1, v2, improvements, whyItWorks, finalPrompt, finalScore)
- Add progress indicator updates during generation (INTENT → BLUEPRINT → GENERATE → SCORE)

**[renderGeneratorResults()](file:///f:/PROMPTLAB/public/js/app.js#581-598) (lines 581-597):**
Complete rewrite to display 5 sections per PRD:

1. **Final Prompt** — generated prompt with copy button, model badge
2. **Auto-Score** — analyzer scores with dimension bars (v1 → v2 if improved)
3. **V1 → V2 Comparison** — side-by-side if auto-improvement triggered
4. **Intent & Blueprint** — collapsible, shows inferred task type/domain/format/control + blueprint schema
5. **Why This Prompt Works** — collapsible educational explanation

### Engine Rebuild

#### [MODIFY] [build-engine.js](file:///f:/PROMPTLAB/build-engine.js)
- No changes needed — already bundles generatorService with analyzerFn wired in

